FT  04 JUN 93 / Howard rejected at Brixton prison
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
OFFICERS at Brixton prison in south London refused yesterday to meet Mr
Michael Howard, home secretary, because of fears about the effect on their
jobs of privatisation of the prisoner-escort service. Mr Howard, on his
