<HEADLINE>
FT  03 JUN 93 / UK Company News: Europe Energy
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Europe Energy, the USM-quoted mining group, incurred a loss of Pounds
132,817 pre-tax for the year to March 31 against a deficit of Pounds 163,953
for the preceding 15 months.
The loss took account of a Pounds 61,855 (nil) provision for the permanent
diminution in value of an oil investment. Losses per share were 1.06p
(1.37p).
